CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 3, 1953, pg. 22 reads: "Fast Action - Shown above are several players who took part in Collegian All-Star-Scholastic All-Star basketball game at Ammon Center last Saturday. The action was fast and furious throughout.  The final score was 70-70."
TitMainTitle: Collegian All-Star-Scholastic All-Star basketball game with player wearing St. Francis t-shirt, at Ammon Center
